data.description: You'll feel right at home right away in this beautiful & bright single-story home located across from Kenilworth Park, less than 2 miles from the New Orleans Lakefront Airport and convenient access to I-10 East & West. With a spacious floor plan & wired for alarm, this home has been well maintained, boasting a new roof in 2021, new hot water heater in 2020 and new AC compressor in 2023.  The primary bedroom has an en-suite bath, large walk in closet and French doors that open to an enclosed sunroom with a wall of windows that lets in the natural light. The kitchen, which includes an eat-in area and bay window, feels like the center of this home connecting the living room & dining room combo & the den. Enjoy time spent inside overlooking your private backyard or step outside and imagine the endless possibilities the unfinished flex space/workspace/extra storage space can be which already includes electricity & the potential for plumbing. The long, gated driveway, which can accommodate multiple vehicles, leads to a carport and covered walkway into the home as well. X flood zone! Don't miss this opportunity to own this beautiful and welcoming home that is just steps away from the neighborhood Park where you can spend time together with friends and family and has features that promote the best of indoor and outdoor living... Start making memories now!! Schedule a showing today!!
